A vintage-style illustration depicting a dramatic drag race between three classic 1960s muscle cars on parallel lanes of a test track, viewed from a low angle emphasizing speed and competition. The cars are positioned side-by-side at the starting line, engines revving with visible heat distortion rising from their hoods. Multiple stopwatches float in the amber sky above like celestial bodies, their hands frozen at different positions. The scene uses warm sepia tones with pops of cherry red and racing green on the vehicles. Film grain texture overlays the entire composition, with subtle vignetting around the edges. The track stretches toward a vanishing point on the horizon, emphasizing the concept of measuring and comparing performance in a tangible, visual way rather than abstract numbers.
